    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到每台计算机都有CloudNative标签，比如A和B是DockerImage，C是K8sCluster，D是HelmChart。Switch本身也是HelmChart类型对吗？",
