      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Switch作为HelmChart。另外我漏了一个角色——还需要CloudNative_ServiceMesh和CloudNative_Serverless，它们会出现在ARP包的标签里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_Serverless",
        "Switch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我按从左到右顺序排列：A（DockerImage）、Switch（HelmChart）、B（DockerImage）、C（K8sCluster）、D（HelmChart）。初始状态需要在Switch上方标注MAC表为空。",
      "elements_involved": [
